  "notes": [
    "This study examined ethnic disparities in male breast cancer burden and healthcare utilization in Inner Mongolia, China",
    "The study found no significant ethnic disparities between Han and Mongolian populations in most outcomes",
    "BRCA mutations, particularly BRCA2, are identified as important risk factors for male breast cancer",
    "Healthcare utilization was relatively low with only 36.8% of patients receiving breast cancer treatments"
  ]
